        <item>
            <title>OpenAI 倡通用人工智能 5 大阶段，表示其人工智能即将进入第 2 阶段</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/openai-ranks-ai-with-5-stages/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=openai-ranks-ai-with-5-stages</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/openai-ranks-ai-with-5-stages/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 15:30:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AGI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[openai]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1249963</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">根据报道指出，OpenAI 已经开发出了一个能够跟进建立通用人工智能（AGI）发展的系统。OpenAI 向旗下员工展示了一个将人工智能分成五个阶段的系统，有助确认人工智能的进展。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1249977 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/bgy6zcgwqasduht74rr3-694x390.jpg" alt="OpenAI" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/bgy6zcgwqasduht74rr3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/bgy6zcgwqasduht74rr3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.tomsguide.com/phones/iphones/openai-could-play-a-role-in-apples-ios-18-update-and-that-has-me-worried">Tom&#8217;s Guide</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">OpenAI 将人工智能分成五大等级，分别是聊天机械人（Chatbots）、能解决人类水平问题的推理者（Reasoners）、能够代表用户采取行动的代理（Agents）、能够帮助发明的创新者（Innovator）和能够完成组织工作的组织者（Organizations）。OpenAI 向员工表示目前公司的进展正处于第一阶段，并有望即将达到第二阶段。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1249978 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/samaltmanreturntoope-694x416.jpg" alt="Sam Altman" width="694" height="416" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/samaltmanreturntoope-694x416.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/samaltmanreturntoope.jpg 1250w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://beebom.com/sam-altman-returns-openai-ceo-new-board-appointed/">Beebom</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">OpenAI 一直致力建构通用人工智能，其提出的五阶段分类系统仍在研究当中，相信会根据得到的反馈意见再进行修改。OpenAI CEO Sam Altman 认为通用人工智能会是人类有史以来创造过最好的工具，他和 OpenAI 技术总监 Mira Murati 在上年十月时曾表示通用人工智能将在未来十年内实现。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.pymnts.com/artificial-intelligence-2/2024/openai-defines-five-steps-from-ai-to-agi/">PYMNTS</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://coingeek.com/openai-faces-probe-in-poland-over-alleged-breach-of-data-protection-rules/">CoinGeek</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/13/openai-strawberry/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">OpenAI Strawberry 增强 AI 推理能力，目标让 AI 达到人类智能水平</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/10/microsoft-ditches-openai-board-observer-seat-amid-regulatory-scrutiny/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">OpenAI 董事会将不加入企业观察员　Microsoft 和 Apple 双双放弃代表席位</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/05/amazfit-zepp-os-4-upgrade-gpt-4o-support/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">多款 Amazfit 智能手表系统更新，将加入 OpenAI GPT-o 多语言模型支援</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/openai-ranks-ai-with-5-stages/ai/">OpenAI 倡通用人工智能 5 大阶段，表示其人工智能即将进入第 2 阶段</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/openai-ranks-ai-with-5-stages/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Apple 开发新「对讲机」技术，毋须连 WiFi 不用上网都可即时群组通话</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/apple-new-walkietalkie-technology-on-iphone/software/iphone-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-new-walkietalkie-technology-on-iphone</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/apple-new-walkietalkie-technology-on-iphone/software/iphone-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 15:00:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone app]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交网络]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AirPods]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[对讲机]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1249928</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 近日就正在开发的一项新技术申请专利，在 Apple 发表的专利申请中详细地介绍了这一项技术，将允许用户使用 iPhone 和 AirPods 与周围的人进行即时通话而无需网络，类似于「对讲机」但双方将能同时互相交谈。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1249935 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1366_20002-694x554.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="554" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1366_20002-694x554.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1366_20002.jpeg 1127w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1249934 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1366_2000-605x580.jpeg" alt="Apple" width="605" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1366_2000-605x580.jpeg 605w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1366_2000.jpeg 939w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 605px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.applesfera.com/rumores/funcion-intercom-homepod-podria-llegar-a-unos-auriculares-nueva-patente">Applesfera</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">这项正在研发的新技术允许用户与单人或多人进行即时通话，在实际使用上的体验会比较像是 AirDrop 但用于通话。AirDrop 容许 iPhone 用户之间分享文件，过程毋需连上网络或云端服务器，而新研发的技术将同样地毋需连上网络或云端服务器便能与用围的用户进行通话。Apple 表示这项技术将会使用 AirTag 用于显示方向和距离的相同技术，在 iPhone 上按距离列出附近的用户，只需点击用户名字即可添加至聊天当中。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">专利的申请中将 iPhone 和 AirPods 作为实现这项新功能的核心技术，预料将会开启一种全新的通讯体验。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料及图片来源：<a href="https://appleinsider.com/articles/24/07/11/apple-is-trying-to-reinvent-group-audio-chat-with-no-cell-or-wifi-needed?utm_medium=rss">AppleInsider</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/27/apple-vision-pro-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e8%a1%8c%e8%b2%a8%e5%85%a8%e6%94%bb%e7%95%a5-%e5%bf%85%e8%a3%9d-app-%e3%80%81-%e6%b8%af%e7%89%88%e7%89%b9%e8%89%b2%e3%80%81%e5%a4%a7%e9%99%b8%e4%bd%bf%e7%94%a8/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Vision Pro 香港行货全攻略 :  必装 APP 、 港版特色、大陆使用、近视及老花用家、预订注意、开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/25/youtube-premium-4/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】继续用外国 YouTube Premium 帐户　路由器内置 VPN、Apple TV、Android TV 连线 VPN</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/apple-vision-pro-preorder-2/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】Apple Vision Pro 香港预订教学　戴眼镜也能轻松买 + 脸部扫描过程</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/apple-new-walkietalkie-technology-on-iphone/software/iphone-app/">Apple 开发新「对讲机」技术，毋须连 WiFi 不用上网都可即时群组通话</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
